WorkflowInfo.Name: INCWorkflow1
WorkflowInfo.Description:
Incident/Ticket management
Checks to see if there are any pending incidents. If there are, an email is send to a group mailbox, if a response is given AND resolution is a success, the incident is resolved. If there is no response OR there has been no resolution, the team will receive an SLA warning.
